you've had all day.

00:14.582 --> 00:15.749
Only on Fox.

00:20.854 --> 00:22.890
-Previously on Empire...
-Angelo is here as my attorney.

00:22.923 --> 00:25.159
-I am suing for sole custody
of Bella. -I need your word

00:25.193 --> 00:27.661
you're not gonna try to take
my baby away from me again.

00:27.695 --> 00:29.597
