know what you want from me.

00:33.867 --> 00:36.270
-I can't lose Bella, Mom.
-And I can't lose you.

00:36.304 --> 00:38.706
-I did some things. -I don't
care what you did, Hakeem.

00:38.739 --> 00:41.075
I'm leaving Empire.
I negotiated for you

00:41.109 --> 00:43.677
-to come with me.
-Who asked you to do that?

00:43.711 --> 00:47.515
-Lucious is gone. It's Dwight.
-No, my name is Lucious.

00:47.548 --> 00:50.017
My office will send you a check.
You may leave now.

00:50.050 --> 00:51.785
I'm back.

