You sure? Come on,
you know I usually warm up

01:36.264 --> 01:38.132
-a lot more than that.
-TONY: Nah, listen,

01:38.166 --> 01:39.967
you sound great, man. It's just
a scratch vocal, anyway.

01:40.000 --> 01:42.069
